data.meta_description: Do we write ten or 10? I have an eight year old son, I have an eight years old son, I have an eight-year-old son, or I have an 8 year old son? What is the best way to write this? In this lesson, I will teach you six common mistakes that students make with numbers, and how to avoid them. We will look at pronunciation, grammar, and writing mistakes.
